*[[Jacques Sernas]] as Gentile
*[[Carlo Ninchi]] as Ciceruacchio
*[[Enzo Cerusico]] as Il figlio di Ciceruacchio
*[[Gino Leurini]] as Andrea
*[[Mario Monosilio]] as Giovanni
*[[Marisa Natale]] as Rosa
*[[Emma Baron]] as La signora Guiccioli
